[normal] I wonder if there is a gap there for the Commons
[normal],
[normal] in terms of the information and pushback provided, and whether some kind of model is needed
[normal].
[normal] 
[normal]B
[normal]ut then you do not want to duplicate and replicate what is going on, so is there a way to try to get that information on Commons starters earlier? You get into fairly tortuous issues around the relationship between the two Houses, but I do think there is a gap there in terms of the material available to this House when it begins scrutinising those.
